    <p>Below is an example of how BaseWeb initiates the class specific styles for dropdowns.</p>
    <pre class="language-scss"><code>.#{map-get($dropdowns, 'class-dropdown')},
.#{map-get($dropdowns, 'class-dropdown-content')},
.#{map-get($dropdowns, 'class-dropdown-menu')} {
  @include make-dropdown();
}
</code></pre>
  </li>
  
